    {"type":"text","id":"beads_consumers","x":1080,"y":1065,"width":220,"height":120,"text":"소비자 스킬:\n  cch-plan   → 생성 (Phase 3)\n  cch-todo   → 조회 (ready 큐)\n  cch-commit → trailer 삽입\n  cch-pr     → PR body 연결\n  cch-team   → 생성/종료\n  cch-full-pipeline → 생성","originalText":"소비자 스킬:\n  cch-plan   → 생성 (Phase 3)\n  cch-todo   → 조회 (ready 큐)\n  cch-commit → trailer 삽입\n  cch-pr     → PR body 연결\n  cch-team   → 생성/종료\n  cch-full-pipeline → 생성","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#374151","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":1106,"version":1,"versionNonce":1107,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
